summary: This mod adds many of the unused NPCs found in the game files.
descriptionHtml:
Many NPCs never made it into the final release of the game, such as College Guards, and Mithorpa Nasyal. This mod aims to change that.
New AI Packages have been given to the newly added NPCs so they can live in their new homes, because their old homes.... never existed. Such as Irontree Mill, which was gonna be home to two unused NPCs. Enjoy the mod!

See how many Now-Added NPCs you can find!
author: kvatchcount
